My son is afraid that I'll get lonely

289
00:12:43,790 --> 00:12:45,240
and wanted me to live with him.

290
00:12:45,670 --> 00:12:46,390
But I think that

291
00:12:46,870 --> 00:12:48,960
the young folks have different habits
from us.

292
00:12:49,270 --> 00:12:50,720
It's more comfortable living on my own.

293
00:12:50,720 --> 00:12:51,270
Yes, yes.

294
00:12:51,270 --> 00:12:51,910
So,

295
00:12:52,670 --> 00:12:53,440
I live alone.

296
00:12:53,670 --> 00:12:54,720
But living alone

297
00:12:55,240 --> 00:12:56,080
has its downsides too.

298
00:12:56,550 --> 00:12:57,240
Where there's nothing to do

299
00:12:57,390 --> 00:12:57,960
