at the screen all day.

303
00:13:02,550 --> 00:13:04,120
That's why I decided to work as a
security guard.

304
00:13:06,440 --> 00:13:07,390
Never would I imagine

305
00:13:08,840 --> 00:13:10,240
that after looking for so long

306
00:13:10,960 --> 00:13:13,270
