307
00:13:13,270 --> 00:13:14,150
yet I didn't notice.

308
00:13:14,440 --> 00:13:14,840
Yes.

309
00:13:15,720 --> 00:13:16,600
Mr. Cai, I'm telling you.

310
00:13:17,120 --> 00:13:18,320
This elderly care project

311
00:13:18,390 --> 00:13:20,720
