325
00:13:46,750 --> 00:13:47,150
How about that?

326
00:13:47,150 --> 00:13:48,630
Alright. I was just joking.

327
00:13:48,870 --> 00:13:49,440
I'll head out first.

328
00:13:49,720 --> 00:13:50,120
Alright.

329
00:13:50,120 --> 00:13:50,630
See you tomorrow.

330
00:13:50,790 --> 00:13:51,840
See you tomorrow.

