338
00:14:08,270 --> 00:14:09,750
It'll be a real milestone.

339
00:14:09,840 --> 00:14:10,270
Yes.

340
00:14:12,150 --> 00:14:12,790
By the way, Ms. Li,

341
00:14:13,270 --> 00:14:14,320
the basic insurance policy

342
00:14:14,320 --> 00:14:16,320
