346
00:14:19,360 --> 00:14:20,320
No need. Cancel it.

347
00:14:22,600 --> 00:14:23,150
Cancel it?

348
00:14:24,030 --> 00:14:24,790
But why?

349
00:14:25,200 --> 00:14:28,030
Originally, TSI slogan is that we focus
on annuities.

350
00:14:28,390 --> 00:14:30,720
We brought in the basic insurance policies

351
