352
00:14:36,790 --> 00:14:37,320
But now,

353
00:14:38,030 --> 00:14:39,600
this type of insurance

354
00:14:39,600 --> 00:14:41,790
no longer aligns with our company's
development strategy.

355
00:14:45,200 --> 00:14:46,150
That may be true,

356
00:14:46,150 --> 00:14:48,080
but keeping this type of insurance

357
00:14:48,080 --> 00:14:49,600
doesn't hurt us, does it?

358
00:14:49,790 --> 00:14:50,910
The board has decided that

359
00:14:51,440 --> 00:14:52,510
all employees in the company

360
00:14:53,080 --> 00:14:55,030
