365
00:15:04,120 --> 00:15:04,670
Besides,

366
00:15:05,440 --> 00:15:08,440
at TSI, we serve high-end clients.

367
00:15:09,120 --> 00:15:10,630
The image we project externally

368
00:15:10,910 --> 00:15:12,120
must be highly professional.

369
00:15:12,630 --> 00:15:15,320
But professionalism isn't just about
the size of the policy.

370
00:15:15,720 --> 00:15:17,750
If not size, then what?

371
00:15:18,910 --> 00:15:21,320
It's about our understanding of the insurance,

372
00:15:21,750 --> 00:15:23,030
the solutions we provide to clients

373
00:15:23,510 --> 00:15:25,600
and also the follow-up services we offer them.

374
00:15:27,630 --> 00:15:29,750
Sharing such vision externally is fine

375
00:15:30,080 --> 00:15:30,870
I have no problem with that.

376
00:15:31,000 --> 00:15:31,480
But internally,

377
00:15:31,960 --> 00:15:33,630
these are just empty talk.

378
00:15:34,320 --> 00:15:35,270
When it comes to sales,

379
00:15:35,670 --> 00:15:37,120
