we're going to wrap things up.

409
00:16:47,750 --> 00:16:49,320
Thanks for all your hard work these past
few days.

410
00:16:49,910 --> 00:16:51,030
I didn't help that much.

411
00:16:51,600 --> 00:16:52,600
You still haven't found a candidate?

412
00:16:53,240 --> 00:16:54,030
No.

413
00:16:54,150 --> 00:16:55,440
The residents in this community

414
00:16:55,440 --> 00:16:56,670
are way too cautious.

415
00:16:57,200 --> 00:16:59,240
Probably because they've been scammed before.

416
00:16:59,600 --> 00:17:01,870
Even a legitimate operation like ours
are being implicated.

417
00:17:01,870 --> 00:17:02,510
Yeah.

418
00:17:03,870 --> 00:17:05,590
Well, I'll be the good guy then.

419
00:17:06,200 --> 00:17:07,590
How about I help you complete this task?

420
00:17:08,830 --> 00:17:10,160
I told you before,

421
00:17:10,160 --> 00:17:11,270
we're promoting this project

422
00:17:11,270 --> 00:17:12,790
not just to complete some task.

423
00:17:13,830 --> 00:17:14,720
Yeah, I know.

424
00:17:15,550 --> 00:17:16,400
I went home one day

425
00:17:16,880 --> 00:17:18,400
and I casually mentioned it to my son.

426
00:17:18,880 --> 00:17:19,590
He was quite happy about it

427
00:17:20,160 --> 00:17:21,880
and said he'd had this idea for a long time.

428
00:17:22,110 --> 00:17:23,310
Just that he didn't know how to bring it up
with me.

429
00:17:24,680 --> 00:17:26,790
Didn't you say your son would scold you?

430
00:17:27,480 --> 00:17:28,310
This time he didn't

431
00:17:29,000 --> 00:17:30,030
He said he's too busy

432
00:17:30,310 --> 00:17:31,110
making money.

433
00:17:32,030 --> 00:17:32,720
