434
00:17:32,720 --> 00:17:33,550
and he feels guilty about it.

435
00:17:33,830 --> 00:17:34,830
Turns out

436
00:17:35,240 --> 00:17:36,310
he's been secretly looking into

437
00:17:36,310 --> 00:17:37,830
several retirement communities.

438
00:17:38,110 --> 00:17:39,160
And they're all quite nice.

439
00:17:39,590 --> 00:17:40,880
He just didn't dare to tell me,
afraid I'd scold him.

440
00:17:41,750 --> 00:17:42,440
and say that he's unfilial.

441
00:17:43,310 --> 00:17:44,960
You've raised a good son.

442
00:17:45,270 --> 00:17:45,830
He's promising.

443
00:17:46,680 --> 00:17:47,440
He keeps up with the trend.

444
00:17:47,510 --> 00:17:48,590
He'll definitely have a bright future.

445
00:17:49,640 --> 00:17:52,110
So, how do I go about the procedure?

446
00:17:53,200 --> 00:17:53,830
Get a physical check-up.

447
00:17:54,000 --> 00:17:55,160
If everything's fine,

448
00:17:55,350 --> 00:17:57,310
you have to go through the process,
and you can check in.

449
00:17:59,680 --> 00:18:00,510
A physical check-up?

450
00:18:01,030 --> 00:18:01,440
Yes.

451
00:18:04,160 --> 00:18:05,110
If that's the case...

452
00:18:05,960 --> 00:18:06,750
Alright.

453
00:18:07,160 --> 00:18:08,750
Where should I get it done?

454
00:18:09,790 --> 00:18:12,440
As long as it's a report from a facility
certified by the government,

455
00:18:12,440 --> 00:18:13,350
We'll accept it.

456
00:18:15,000 --> 00:18:15,510
Mr. Cai,

457
00:18:15,880 --> 00:18:17,070
if you're interested,

458
00:18:17,240 --> 00:18:18,720
