459
00:18:19,590 --> 00:18:20,480
Here, Mr. Cai.

460
00:18:20,640 --> 00:18:21,920
Come, sit down while you fill it out.

461
00:18:21,920 --> 00:18:22,310
Here's a pen.

462
00:18:22,550 --> 00:18:23,200
Here, take a seat.

463
00:18:23,200 --> 00:18:24,240
Come, sit down and fill it out.

464
00:18:26,350 --> 00:18:27,270
Fill in your name.

465
00:18:30,680 --> 00:18:31,350
Gender.

466
00:18:41,310 --> 00:18:41,590
Here you go.

467
00:18:41,590 --> 00:18:42,070
Dad!

468
00:18:42,200 --> 00:18:42,750
Have another bite.

469
00:18:42,880 --> 00:18:43,590
I'm here.

470
00:18:44,350 --> 00:18:45,160
Why were you looking for me?

471
00:18:45,160 --> 00:18:45,960
What's so urgent?

472
00:18:46,480 --> 00:18:47,440
Are you not feeling well?

473
00:18:51,110 --> 00:18:51,640
Ms. Hu,

474
00:18:52,270 --> 00:18:53,680
he talks about you all day.

475
00:18:54,030 --> 00:18:55,270
He's not doing his rehab seriously,

476
00:18:55,400 --> 00:18:56,510
and he's not eating properly either.

477
00:18:57,790 --> 00:18:58,960
What's going on with you?

478
00:18:59,550 --> 00:19:00,680
Didn't I tell you

479
00:19:00,680 --> 00:19:01,830
I'm busy this month

480
00:19:01,920 --> 00:19:03,590
Once I get through this, things will be fine.

481
00:19:04,510 --> 00:19:05,160
Sorry

482
00:19:05,160 --> 00:19:05,830
and thank you.

483
00:19:06,070 --> 00:19:06,400
It's okay.

484
00:19:06,400 --> 00:19:07,030
You two talk it out.

485
00:19:07,240 --> 00:19:08,350
Okay, thank you.

486
00:19:11,110 --> 00:19:11,790
What are you getting?

487
00:19:14,400 --> 00:19:15,680
Here.

488
00:19:16,640 --> 00:19:17,790
Why are you giving me money?

489
00:19:18,160 --> 00:19:19,680
Go

490
00:19:20,880 --> 00:19:21,510
and buy

491
00:19:22,200 --> 00:19:23,070
a piece of cream cake.

492
00:19:25,640 --> 00:19:27,240
You made me take a long ride

493
00:19:28,350 --> 00:19:30,550
all the way from Puxi to Pudong

494
00:19:30,550 --> 00:19:31,680
just to give me money

495
00:19:32,240 --> 00:19:33,270
to help you buy a cake?

496
00:19:34,240 --> 00:19:35,270
You can't eat it.

497
00:19:35,720 --> 00:19:37,070
Your blood sugar level just got better.

498
00:19:37,070 --> 00:19:38,160
Don't mess around.

499
00:19:38,160 --> 00:19:40,440
