504
00:19:51,880 --> 00:19:52,790
Have you forgotten?

505
00:19:55,350 --> 00:19:56,000
What day is it today?

506
00:20:02,030 --> 00:20:02,640
You're right.

507
00:20:04,030 --> 00:20:05,110
Even I have forgotten it.

508
00:20:09,270 --> 00:20:10,200
This is

509
00:20:11,110 --> 00:20:12,240
a big deal.

510
00:20:12,350 --> 00:20:13,830
I remember it clearly.

511
00:20:14,640 --> 00:20:15,830
40 years old.

512
00:20:17,720 --> 00:20:19,440
What's there to celebrate at 40? I'm old.

513
00:20:20,000 --> 00:20:22,270
In my heart,

514
00:20:23,750 --> 00:20:26,240
yo...you'll always be my little girl.

515
00:20:27,880 --> 00:20:29,350
Other people might forget,

516
00:20:30,350 --> 00:20:30,750
But I...

517
00:20:31,400 --> 00:20:31,750
I...

518
00:20:32,510 --> 00:20:35,160
I can't forget, right?

519
00:20:36,750 --> 00:20:38,240
40 years old and still a young lady.

520
00:20:38,590 --> 00:20:40,110
You're making me cry.

521
00:20:40,160 --> 00:20:40,830
You really are...

522
00:20:45,070 --> 00:20:49,880
Happy birthday to you...

523
00:20:50,200 --> 00:20:53,640
Happy birthday to you...

524
00:20:55,440 --> 00:20:56,590
Alright, stop crying.

525
00:20:58,400 --> 00:20:59,590
Dad's the only one who's good to me.

526
00:21:00,030 --> 00:21:00,640
I'll give you a kiss.

527
00:21:06,590 --> 00:21:07,640
No, it's not.

528
00:21:09,160 --> 00:21:09,640
It's not?

529
00:21:10,200 --> 00:21:11,200
It's alright.

530
00:21:14,160 --> 00:21:16,270
One, two, three.

531
00:23:04,310 --> 00:23:05,110
Happy birthday!

532
00:23:19,590 --> 00:23:20,750
Mom, don't turn on the light.

533
00:23:21,310 --> 00:23:24,680
Happy birthday to you,

534
00:23:25,160 --> 00:23:28,160
Happy birthday to you,

535
00:23:28,960 --> 00:23:32,590
Happy birthday to you,

536
00:23:32,790 --> 00:23:35,590
Happy birthday to you.

537
00:23:35,590 --> 00:23:36,510
Ms. Hu Manli,

538
00:23:36,720 --> 00:23:38,000
