539
00:23:38,110 --> 00:23:40,680
From now on, you're someone who's heading
into your fifties.

540
00:23:41,480 --> 00:23:42,270
Dear bestie,

541
00:23:42,270 --> 00:23:43,510
mind your words, will you?

542
00:23:44,310 --> 00:23:44,680
Look,

543
00:23:44,680 --> 00:23:47,200
we made this cake specially for you.

544
00:23:47,440 --> 00:23:48,270
Make a wish!

545
00:23:57,880 --> 00:23:58,680
You blew really hard!

546
00:23:59,030 --> 00:24:00,200
Happy birthday!

547
00:24:00,200 --> 00:24:01,270
Thank you.

548
00:24:02,550 --> 00:24:03,590
This is my birthday gift for you.

549
00:24:04,000 --> 00:24:04,790
Thank you.

550
00:24:04,790 --> 00:24:06,720
You've really raised a thoughtful son.

551
00:24:06,960 --> 00:24:07,880
He told me about your birthday

552
00:24:07,880 --> 00:24:09,480
a week in advance,

553
00:24:09,720 --> 00:24:11,160
