for you.

554
00:24:11,350 --> 00:24:12,240
He said that

555
00:24:12,240 --> 00:24:13,480
this is your favorite flavor.

556
00:24:13,790 --> 00:24:14,720
He even told me to keep it a secret

557
00:24:14,750 --> 00:24:16,000
because he wanted to give you a surprise.

558
00:24:16,270 --> 00:24:16,880
Are you touched?

559
00:24:17,400 --> 00:24:18,510
So this is my favorite flavor?

560
00:24:19,240 --> 00:24:20,750
I think you're just craving it.

561
00:24:21,640 --> 00:24:23,350
Next time, don't surprise me like that.

562
00:24:23,350 --> 00:24:24,750
I'm getting older, and my heart can't take
surprises like that.

563
00:24:25,640 --> 00:24:26,440
You're stubborn as always.

564
00:24:26,790 --> 00:24:28,550
Who else would remember your birthday but us?

565
00:24:28,720 --> 00:24:29,240
Am I right, Daer?

566
00:24:30,240 --> 00:24:31,750
Plenty of people remember my birthday!

567
00:24:31,920 --> 00:24:32,480
Like who?

568
00:24:32,830 --> 00:24:34,920
The bank? Beauty salons? Insurance companies?

569
00:24:35,240 --> 00:24:36,400
