am I right?

570
00:24:36,480 --> 00:24:37,030
Who said so?

571
00:24:37,680 --> 00:24:38,880
My dad remembers my birthday!

572
00:24:39,310 --> 00:24:39,640
And also...

573
00:24:39,640 --> 00:24:40,160
And also my dad!

574
00:24:40,680 --> 00:24:42,160
My dad sent you a birthday message, didn't he?

