00:24:42,480 --> 00:24:43,200
He told me about it.

576
00:24:43,550 --> 00:24:44,160
You're a smart one, aren't you?

577
00:24:45,240 --> 00:24:46,030
Come, take a seat.

578
00:24:50,790 --> 00:24:52,240
Did your little brother get you anything?

579
00:24:53,070 --> 00:24:53,920
I'm an only child.

580
00:24:54,350 --> 00:24:55,270
I don't have a little brother.

581
00:24:57,070 --> 00:24:58,480
Xiaozhou wouldn't forget it, would he?

582
00:24:58,830 --> 00:25:00,000
Quickly eat your pizza.

583
00:25:00,000 --> 00:25:01,400
Then go finish your homework.

584
00:25:03,110 --> 00:25:03,880
Seriously?

585
00:25:04,480 --> 00:25:05,960
He didn't even send a "Happy Birthday"?

586
00:25:07,200 --> 00:25:08,030
It makes sense.

587
00:25:08,030 --> 00:25:09,440
I was very harsh the last time we spoke.

588
00:25:09,960 --> 00:25:11,590
He probably never wants to see me again.

589
00:25:18,030 --> 00:25:18,480
What's wrong?

590
00:25:43,110 --> 00:25:43,880
Happy birthday.

591
00:25:47,270 --> 00:25:48,590
What a beautiful cake.

592
00:25:49,510 --> 00:25:50,000
It is.

593
00:25:50,000 --> 00:25:51,920
I don't even know where to put the candles.

594
00:25:53,240 --> 00:25:55,000
Then don't ruin it.

595
00:25:55,920 --> 00:25:57,510
I already made a wish just now

596
00:25:57,790 --> 00:25:58,590
and blew out the candles.

597
00:25:59,550 --> 00:26:01,240
Alright then. Take it home and eat it
with Ding.

598
00:26:01,720 --> 00:26:02,200
Thank you.

599
00:26:04,160 --> 00:26:04,480
Oh, right.

600
00:26:07,480 --> 00:26:08,160
Your birthday present.

601
00:26:08,960 --> 00:26:09,750
There's a present too?

602
00:26:11,160 --> 00:26:11,680
Thank you.

603
00:26:14,480 --> 00:26:15,310
All you say is "Thank you"?

604
00:26:15,480 --> 00:26:16,400
Are you not going to open it?

605
00:27:23,480 --> 00:27:24,480
You really

606
00:27:25,030 --> 00:27:26,510
went all out,

607
00:27:26,510 --> 00:27:28,240
and tore them into pieces.

608
00:27:28,680 --> 00:27:30,110
I worked really hard to put them back together.

609
00:27:39,240 --> 00:27:39,720
Hu Manli,

610
00:27:41,240 --> 00:27:42,070
I've figured it out.

611
00:27:44,310 --> 00:27:45,160
I'll use

612
00:27:46,110 --> 00:27:47,640
the method that you like to interact with you.

613
00:27:48,920 --> 00:27:49,680
You think

614
00:27:50,110 --> 00:27:50,960
I'm not mature enough.

615
00:27:51,960 --> 00:27:52,590
It's okay.

616
00:27:53,110 --> 00:27:54,000
I'll work on it.

617
00:27:55,310 --> 00:27:55,960
You said

618
00:27:56,640 --> 00:27:58,240
you don't want to be in a relationship
right now.

619
00:27:59,160 --> 00:27:59,880
That's fine too.

620
00:28:00,590 --> 00:28:01,240
I can wait for you.

621
00:28:02,030 --> 00:28:03,030
A year or two,

622
00:28:03,070 --> 00:28:04,000
if not, then three years.

623
00:28:04,310 --> 00:28:05,400
And even if it takes 5 years

624
00:28:06,070 --> 00:28:07,240
I'll always be by your side.

625
00:28:12,830 --> 00:28:13,480
Xiaozhou,

626
00:28:15,790 --> 00:28:17,440
I'm 11 years older than you.

627
00:28:18,640 --> 00:28:20,350
And I'll only keep aging.

628
00:28:20,790 --> 00:28:21,790
You're already old.

629
00:28:25,240 --> 00:28:26,400
Mind your words, will you?

630
00:28:26,440 --> 00:28:27,510
It's my birthday today.

631
00:28:27,920 --> 00:28:29,350
Or else you'll never close a deal in your life.

632
00:28:30,310 --> 00:28:31,350
You're scolding me again.

633
00:28:32,070 --> 00:28:33,400
The moonlight's so pretty tonight.

634
00:28:33,400 --> 00:28:34,790
Maybe you should scold me a bit more.

635
00:28:35,240 --> 00:28:36,070
That'll cost you.

636
00:28:40,830 --> 00:28:42,000
Hu Manli, I still want to say this.

637
00:28:43,640 --> 00:28:44,160
I'm sorry.

638
00:28:45,480 --> 00:28:46,070
In the past,

639
00:28:46,720 --> 00:28:48,110
I've caused you quite a bit of trouble.

640
00:28:49,880 --> 00:28:51,590
I also want to thank you
for teaching me so much.

641
00:28:52,960 --> 00:28:53,350
No,

642
00:28:54,400 --> 00:28:55,590
I should be the one thanking you.

643
00:29:00,070 --> 00:29:01,920
During the hardest time in my life,

644
00:29:02,790 --> 00:29:04,030
It was you who helped me through it.

645
00:29:05,590 --> 00:29:06,510
Because of you,

646
00:29:08,110 --> 00:29:09,350
when I look back into the past,

647
00:29:10,680 --> 00:29:11,640
I can still smile.

648
00:29:14,960 --> 00:29:16,000
We're still friends, aren't we?

649
00:29:21,440 --> 00:29:22,720
I really like the present.

650
00:29:23,350 --> 00:29:24,070
Thank you.

651
00:29:24,680 --> 00:29:25,350
Good friend.

652
00:29:29,310 --> 00:29:30,720
Let me ask you a question.

653
00:29:32,310 --> 00:29:32,830
Go ahead.

654
00:29:34,200 --> 00:29:35,550
Why did you decide to return to Blue Ocean?

655
00:29:38,680 --> 00:29:39,400
Because...

656
00:29:42,200 --> 00:29:43,640
I want to do the right thing.

657
00:29:51,830 --> 00:29:52,240
I understand.

658
00:30:19,590 --> 00:30:20,160
Ms. Hu,

659
00:30:21,440 --> 00:30:24,200
there's something wrong with Mr. Cai's
medical report.

660
00:30:24,750 --> 00:30:25,550
What is it?

661
00:30:26,200 --> 00:30:29,160
Did he fail one of the health indicators?

662
00:30:29,880 --> 00:30:30,480
The report is fake.

663
00:30:33,590 --> 00:30:34,240
No way.

664
00:30:35,920 --> 00:30:36,750
The underwriting department

665
00:30:37,790 --> 00:30:39,110
hasn't confirmed it with me yet.

666
00:30:41,640 --> 00:30:42,310
Ms. Hu,

667
00:30:43,240 --> 00:30:44,680
you need to look into this carefully.

668
00:30:45,110 --> 00:30:46,510
Insurance fraud is not a minor offense.

669
00:30:51,000 --> 00:30:51,440
Right.

670
00:30:52,750 --> 00:30:53,750
I'll investigate it.

671
00:30:55,640 --> 00:30:57,030
I'll go find Mr. Cai right away.

672
00:31:09,830 --> 00:31:10,510
Mr. Cai.

673
00:31:12,310 --> 00:31:12,830
Ms. Hu.

674
00:31:13,310 --> 00:31:13,920
You're here.

675
00:31:14,440 --> 00:31:16,750
Are you here to notify me to get ready
to move in?

676
00:31:19,110 --> 00:31:19,830
Mr. Cai,

677
00:31:20,270 --> 00:31:24,830
the company says that there's a problem
with the medical report you provided.

678
00:31:25,790 --> 00:31:26,720
What is it?

679
00:31:34,000 --> 00:31:35,110
It hasn't been that long.

680
00:31:35,750 --> 00:31:36,790
It's only been a year or two.

681
00:31:37,440 --> 00:31:38,440
I'm in good health.

682
00:31:39,030 --> 00:31:41,200
I walk over 10,000 steps a day
in the neighborhood.

683
00:31:41,240 --> 00:31:42,110
Everyone knows that.

684
00:31:43,000 --> 00:31:43,720
Mr. Cai,

685
00:31:44,510 --> 00:31:45,590
our underwriting department

686
00:31:45,590 --> 00:31:46,480
can access

687
00:31:46,480 --> 00:31:49,030
your hospital records

688
00:31:50,030 --> 00:31:52,310
Your health isn't as good as you said it is.

689
00:31:53,000 --> 00:31:54,240
And it's not a small issue.

690
00:31:55,440 --> 00:31:56,830
Concealing information to get insured,

691
00:31:57,350 --> 00:31:58,550
can have serious consequences.

692
00:32:00,110 --> 00:32:01,680
Insurance fraud is illegal.

693
00:32:04,030 --> 00:32:05,550
It's just free accommodation,

694
00:32:05,550 --> 00:32:06,790
do you have to make a big deal out of it?

695
00:32:07,680 --> 00:32:09,240
I wasn't doing it for the free accommodation.

696
00:32:09,720 --> 00:32:10,880
I only wanted to help you.

697
00:32:11,960 --> 00:32:13,350
I appreciate your good intentions.

698
00:32:14,640 --> 00:32:15,590
How about this?

699
00:32:16,310 --> 00:32:18,310
Please come with me to the company

700
00:32:18,790 --> 00:32:19,920
to explain the situation.

701
00:32:20,350 --> 00:32:21,790
Let's try to minimize the consequences

702
00:32:21,790 --> 00:32:23,000
and resolve the matter.

703
00:32:23,350 --> 00:32:24,000
I'm not going.

704
00:32:25,000 --> 00:32:26,070
I didn't deceive you.

705
00:32:27,030 --> 00:32:28,160
I don't need to explain anything.

706
00:32:33,510 --> 00:32:34,160
Mr. Cai,

707
00:32:35,030 --> 00:32:35,830
I don't know

708
00:32:35,830 --> 00:32:38,110
why you choose to deceive me.

709
00:32:38,880 --> 00:32:39,830
But during this time,

710
00:32:40,440 --> 00:32:42,310
we've spent quite a bit of time together.

711
00:32:43,440 --> 00:32:45,350
I know what kind of person you are.

712
00:32:45,830 --> 00:32:47,750
You're honest and genuine.

713
00:32:48,720 --> 00:32:50,720
If you're going through something difficult,
you can tell me.

714
00:32:52,110 --> 00:32:53,680
Maybe I can help you.

715
00:33:01,400 --> 00:33:02,110
It's stomach cancer.

716
00:33:03,350 --> 00:33:04,440
How can you help me?

717
00:33:16,270 --> 00:33:17,510
What did the doctor say?

718
00:33:19,960 --> 00:33:20,680
It's incurable.

719
00:33:21,920 --> 00:33:22,960
I can only live for at most one
or two years.

720
00:33:29,070 --> 00:33:29,680
Take it slow.

721
00:33:30,070 --> 00:33:30,920
You too.

722
00:33:32,110 --> 00:33:32,590
Be careful.

723
00:33:32,590 --> 00:33:33,200
It's okay.

724
00:33:34,830 --> 00:33:35,160
Here.

725
00:33:39,590 --> 00:33:40,070
This is it.

726
00:33:50,350 --> 00:33:51,550
Please come in.

727
00:34:08,880 --> 00:34:10,550
There's no window in this room

728
00:34:11,960 --> 00:34:13,440
and the basement has poor ventilation.

729
00:34:15,920 --> 00:34:18,440
Your health condition is not suitable
for living here.

730
00:34:20,280 --> 00:34:21,070
Please have a seat.

731
00:34:21,510 --> 00:34:22,030
Please sit.

732
00:34:22,590 --> 00:34:22,920
Take a seat.

733
00:34:29,670 --> 00:34:30,590
I've already lived here

734
00:34:31,320 --> 00:34:32,440
for over 20 years.

735
00:34:33,230 --> 00:34:34,590
I don't mind another year or two.

736
00:34:35,280 --> 00:34:35,800
Ms. Hu,

737
00:34:36,800 --> 00:34:38,880
I didn't go to the company to explain myself

738
00:34:39,320 --> 00:34:41,110
mainly because I'm afraid that others
will find out about my illness,

739
00:34:41,360 --> 00:34:42,440
and I'll lose my job.

740
00:34:51,760 --> 00:34:53,070
Does your son know about your illness?

741
00:34:54,030 --> 00:34:55,070
He'll know sooner or later.

742
00:34:55,510 --> 00:34:56,550
You should tell him.

743
00:34:57,800 --> 00:34:58,960
What good would that do?

744
00:34:59,840 --> 00:35:00,590
He's not god.

745
00:35:01,000 --> 00:35:01,880
Can he cure my illness?

746
00:35:02,550 --> 00:35:04,440
Telling him will only add to his burden.

747
00:35:04,920 --> 00:35:06,960
In the end, he'll lose both money and hope.

748
00:35:07,150 --> 00:35:07,760
This at least

749
00:35:08,230 --> 00:35:09,190
I know.

750
00:35:09,550 --> 00:35:10,440
Don't say that.

751
00:35:10,440 --> 00:35:12,000
If you're sick, you should treat it first.

752
00:35:12,230 --> 00:35:13,630
Medical treatment is so advanced nowadays.

753
00:35:14,000 --> 00:35:15,440
As long as the cancer cell hasn't spread,

754
00:35:15,440 --> 00:35:16,550
there's still hope.

755
00:35:19,550 --> 00:35:20,110
Ms. Hu,

756
00:35:21,670 --> 00:35:22,710
I don't have social insurance.

757
00:35:23,190 --> 00:35:24,510
Every penny I spend on treatment,

758
00:35:25,280 --> 00:35:26,320
comes out of my own pocket.

759
00:35:27,000 --> 00:35:28,030
To have lived until today...

760
00:35:29,400 --> 00:35:29,800
Honestly,

761
00:35:30,230 --> 00:35:31,280
I'm kind of proud of myself.

762
00:35:31,800 --> 00:35:32,440
My children

763
00:35:32,880 --> 00:35:33,840
are all married and have their careers now.

764
00:35:34,110 --> 00:35:35,670
They even have kids of their own.

765
00:35:36,880 --> 00:35:38,070
Even if I die now,

766
00:35:38,320 --> 00:35:39,440
I'd be at peace.

767
00:35:40,480 --> 00:35:41,800
But I feel aggrieved.

768
00:35:43,000 --> 00:35:45,230
I've been struggling in Shanghai
for over 20 years.

769
00:35:46,150 --> 00:35:47,000
Yet I didn't manage to make any money.

770
00:35:48,070 --> 00:35:49,630
I've been living in this basement
the whole time.

771
00:35:50,360 --> 00:35:51,030
All I hoped for

772
00:35:52,110 --> 00:35:53,110
before I die

773
00:35:53,960 --> 00:35:54,760
is to live in

774
00:35:55,440 --> 00:35:56,800
a room with a window.

775
00:35:57,880 --> 00:35:58,710
That would be enough for me.

776
00:36:00,030 --> 00:36:00,840
So I...

777
00:36:01,000 --> 00:36:02,320
So you deceived us.

778
00:36:02,800 --> 00:36:03,550
You're good to your son

779
00:36:03,550 --> 00:36:04,630
but cruel to strangers...

780
00:36:08,590 --> 00:36:09,710
Say whatever you want.

781
00:36:10,920 --> 00:36:11,630
I'm already

782
00:36:12,070 --> 00:36:13,030
on the verge of death.

783
00:36:13,360 --> 00:36:14,880
I don't care what others think of me.

784
00:36:16,480 --> 00:36:17,510
All my life

785
00:36:17,840 --> 00:36:18,880
I've worked honestly

786
00:36:19,150 --> 00:36:20,030
and lived with integrity.

787
00:36:21,440 --> 00:36:22,800
I should be considered a good person, right?

788
00:36:24,190 --> 00:36:24,550
But...

789
00:36:25,230 --> 00:36:26,800
how did I end up like this?

790
00:36:30,190 --> 00:36:31,280
Everything is fake.

791
00:36:32,550 --> 00:36:33,320
Before I die...

792
00:36:34,360 --> 00:36:34,880
if only

793
00:36:35,360 --> 00:36:36,920
I could enjoy a few good days.

794
00:36:37,960 --> 00:36:39,630
Even criminals who are to be executed,

795
00:36:39,960 --> 00:36:41,510
get to eat a good last meal,

796
00:36:42,150 --> 00:36:42,590
don't they?

797
00:36:44,710 --> 00:36:45,400
To tell you the truth,

798
00:36:45,800 --> 00:36:47,800
when you first came to our neighborhood
to promote your project,

799
00:36:49,550 --> 00:36:51,110
When I saw your

800
00:36:51,710 --> 00:36:52,800
nursing home poster,

801
00:36:54,550 --> 00:36:55,920
I was captivated by it.

802
00:36:56,710 --> 00:36:57,710
Such a nice room.

803
00:36:58,510 --> 00:36:59,880
A sunny bedroom with windows,

804
00:37:00,480 --> 00:37:02,150
and lush greenery outside.

805
00:37:03,630 --> 00:37:04,590
I thought to myself right then,

806
00:37:06,030 --> 00:37:07,230
if I could just

807
00:37:07,880 --> 00:37:10,000
spend one night in a room like that

808
00:37:11,000 --> 00:37:12,110
and die the next day,

809
00:37:12,480 --> 00:37:13,550
I'd have no regrets.

810
00:37:25,320 --> 00:37:25,920
Mr. Cai,

811
00:37:28,150 --> 00:37:30,280
you can tell me about your thoughts.

812
00:37:30,920 --> 00:37:32,510
Telling even the Emperor wouldn't help.

813
00:37:33,190 --> 00:37:34,230
A person's entire life

814
00:37:34,760 --> 00:37:35,800
it's all for one word:

815
00:37:36,760 --> 00:37:37,230
Money.

816
00:37:38,320 --> 00:37:39,320
If you don't make money,

817
00:37:40,150 --> 00:37:40,840
all your efforts

818
00:37:41,840 --> 00:37:42,510
will be wasted

819
00:37:43,630 --> 00:37:45,110
and your whole life will have no meaning.

820
00:37:51,000 --> 00:37:51,800
Today,

821
00:37:52,480 --> 00:37:54,190
I want to share a story with all of you.

822
00:37:55,590 --> 00:37:57,840
"The Last Window of Life"

823
00:38:00,550 --> 00:38:01,800
Everyone has dreams.

824
00:38:03,280 --> 00:38:04,070
Some people

825
00:38:04,230 --> 00:38:06,710
hope to achieve fame and success;

826
00:38:07,710 --> 00:38:08,550
Some

827
00:38:10,760 --> 00:38:12,110
wants to earn big money

828
00:38:13,550 --> 00:38:14,400
And some people,

829
00:38:14,920 --> 00:38:18,030
just want to be safe and healthy.

830
00:38:19,800 --> 00:38:20,630
A few days ago,

831
00:38:21,190 --> 00:38:23,880
I heard of a heartbreaking dream.

832
00:38:26,070 --> 00:38:26,880
It's about someone

833
00:38:26,880 --> 00:38:29,030
who struggled in this city for over 20 years,

834
00:38:29,960 --> 00:38:30,880
living in a basement

835
00:38:31,320 --> 00:38:32,760
for half a lifetime.

836
00:38:36,000 --> 00:38:37,230
He has a terminal illness.

837
00:38:39,150 --> 00:38:40,070
His dream

838
00:38:41,000 --> 00:38:42,760
is that in the time he has left

839
00:38:43,550 --> 00:38:46,150
he could live in a room with a window.

840
00:38:49,510 --> 00:38:50,070
Alright, no problem.

841
00:38:50,110 --> 00:38:50,960
I'll go welcome him in a bit.

842
00:38:51,550 --> 00:38:52,710
Mr. Zhang has instructed it.

843
00:38:55,070 --> 00:38:55,480
Come in.

844
00:39:00,670 --> 00:39:01,110
Okay.

845
00:39:02,070 --> 00:39:03,230
You owe me a meal.

846
00:39:05,150 --> 00:39:05,670
It's settled then.

847
00:39:08,190 --> 00:39:08,880
Alright, you're welcome

848
00:39:10,280 --> 00:39:10,710
Goodbye.

849
00:39:16,480 --> 00:39:17,000
Xiaozhou,

850
00:39:18,230 --> 00:39:19,710
if your father could see what
you've achieved today,

851
00:39:20,710 --> 00:39:21,920
he would be so proud of you.

852
00:39:23,480 --> 00:39:24,000
Come, have a seat.

853
00:39:30,030 --> 00:39:30,480
Say,

854
00:39:31,000 --> 00:39:31,670
why are you here?

855
00:39:32,670 --> 00:39:33,710
I believe you've heard

856
00:39:34,190 --> 00:39:36,030
about Zhig's situation.

857
00:39:36,710 --> 00:39:38,670
Xiaozhou, you know a lot of people.

858
00:39:39,590 --> 00:39:41,480
Your dad's company needs your help.

859
00:39:42,800 --> 00:39:44,590
Just two million yuan

860
00:39:44,840 --> 00:39:46,360
and the institution won't sue the company.

861
00:39:48,150 --> 00:39:50,190
This amount is only a drop in the bucket,

862
00:39:50,630 --> 00:39:51,800
for your clients.

863
00:39:53,150 --> 00:39:53,920
Qiu Lisu,

864
00:39:54,590 --> 00:39:56,070
you still owe me money, remember?

865
00:39:56,710 --> 00:39:58,360
You said 3 million a month.

866
00:39:58,710 --> 00:40:00,230
In the end, I only received
three hundred thousand yuan.

867
00:40:00,280 --> 00:40:01,400
I haven't even asked you to pay that back.

868
00:40:02,280 --> 00:40:03,760
If I had any other way,

869
00:40:03,960 --> 00:40:05,150
I wouldn't be here begging you.

870
00:40:05,400 --> 00:40:07,510
As long as you help Zhig get through
this crisis,

871
00:40:08,480 --> 00:40:09,760
I'll pay you back.

872
00:40:11,480 --> 00:40:12,710
I think you're quite pitiful,

873
00:40:13,840 --> 00:40:14,190
really.

874
00:40:17,480 --> 00:40:19,000
Are you going to scold me on behalf of Hu Manli?

875
00:40:19,400 --> 00:40:19,960
It's fine.

876
00:40:21,800 --> 00:40:24,550
I've heard worse throughout the years.

877
00:40:24,760 --> 00:40:25,280
Go ahead and scold me.

878
00:40:27,510 --> 00:40:28,400
This has nothing to do with her.

879
00:40:30,070 --> 00:40:31,320
It's just that you want too much.

880
00:40:33,000 --> 00:40:34,000
You want money,

881
00:40:34,400 --> 00:40:36,190
love,

882
00:40:36,880 --> 00:40:37,630
reputation,

883
00:40:38,360 --> 00:40:41,110
and to prove to the world that Qiu Lisu
is capable.

884
00:40:41,320 --> 00:40:42,510
You think you deserve to have it all.

885
00:40:43,670 --> 00:40:44,510
Isn't living like this

886
00:40:45,030 --> 00:40:46,360
truly exhausting?

887
00:40:47,150 --> 00:40:47,840
Xue Xiaozhou

888
00:40:49,320 --> 00:40:50,800
you can say that I have no morals.

889
00:40:52,000 --> 00:40:53,070
I chose this path,

890
00:40:53,630 --> 00:40:55,670
so I don't care what others think.

891
00:40:57,550 --> 00:40:59,440
But you cannot deny my ability,

892
00:40:59,710 --> 00:41:00,510
my value.

893
00:41:01,030 --> 00:41:02,670
When your dad was at his lowest,

894
00:41:02,880 --> 00:41:04,440
I was the one who stuck with him through it.

895
00:41:05,510 --> 00:41:06,670
After he passed away,

896
00:41:07,030 --> 00:41:09,190
I was the only one who support Zhig alone.

897
00:41:09,880 --> 00:41:10,800
Even until now,

898
00:41:11,630 --> 00:41:13,150
I know you hate me

899
00:41:13,150 --> 00:41:13,840
and loathe me,

900
00:41:13,840 --> 00:41:15,150
but I can still stand here

901
00:41:16,280 --> 00:41:17,920
to be you

902
00:41:18,710 --> 00:41:19,510
What dignity,

903
00:41:19,710 --> 00:41:20,440
what pride,

904
00:41:21,230 --> 00:41:22,440
if I can save the company

905
00:41:22,920 --> 00:41:24,320
I'm willing to give it all up.

906
00:41:27,510 --> 00:41:27,920
Fine then.

907
00:41:28,320 --> 00:41:28,880
Let's

908
00:41:29,800 --> 00:41:30,670
talk business.

909
00:41:31,150 --> 00:41:31,550
Alright.

910
00:41:32,230 --> 00:41:33,070
Our house

911
00:41:34,110 --> 00:41:35,030
were taken by you.

912
00:41:35,920 --> 00:41:37,150
You took it to fill the company's hole.

913
00:41:37,960 --> 00:41:40,150
My dad's inheritance was used up too.

914
00:41:40,630 --> 00:41:41,880
Now you're asking me for two million yuan?

915
00:41:42,480 --> 00:41:43,440
Fine, what about next time?

916
00:41:43,920 --> 00:41:44,440
Three million yen?

917
00:41:44,480 --> 00:41:45,670
And the time after that, 5 million?

918
00:41:46,150 --> 00:41:46,760
Qiu Lisu, have you ever

919
00:41:46,760 --> 00:41:47,800
considered this.

920
00:41:48,070 --> 00:41:49,320
If a company

921
00:41:49,960 --> 00:41:51,840
has to rely on constant infusion

922
00:41:52,000 --> 00:41:53,150
just to survive,

923
00:41:53,510 --> 00:41:54,400
Shouldn't you consider

924
00:41:55,280 --> 00:41:56,440
pulling the plug?

925
00:41:57,480 --> 00:41:58,550
That way, you'd be free too.

926
00:42:01,030 --> 00:42:02,030
You're not going to help?

927
00:42:20,590 --> 00:42:21,920
Ding Zhiyuan is going to divorce me.

928
00:42:22,760 --> 00:42:23,550
Actually, both of them

929
00:42:24,440 --> 00:42:25,840
have been thinking of reconciling.

930
00:42:29,480 --> 00:42:30,670
For a women like that,

931
00:42:32,030 --> 00:42:32,590
is it really worth it?

932
00:42:37,480 --> 00:42:38,030
Everyone

933
00:42:38,670 --> 00:42:40,400
eventually has to pay

934
00:42:41,480 --> 00:42:42,230
for their choices.

935
00:42:45,760 --> 00:42:46,230
I still have matters to attend to.

936
00:42:47,920 --> 00:42:48,320
Lingling,

937
00:42:49,320 --> 00:42:49,960
see her out for me.

938
00:42:51,030 --> 00:42:51,400
Madam,

939
00:42:51,960 --> 00:42:52,480
this way please.

940
00:43:06,680 --> 00:43:08,560
♪If I close both eyes tonight♪

941
00:43:08,560 --> 00:43:12,440
♪Back to that wishing summer night♪

942
00:43:12,440 --> 00:43:16,200
♪Wind brushes your shaking frame♪

943
00:43:16,200 --> 00:43:21,000
♪That world feels close just the same♪

944
00:43:21,000 --> 00:43:23,400
♪If I dare to face the dawn♪

945
00:43:23,400 --> 00:43:27,120
♪Do you know this face you'd drawn♪

946
00:43:27,120 --> 00:43:30,920
♪Gray spirals looped in endless chase♪

947
00:43:30,920 --> 00:43:35,720
♪Tracing tears not words they trace♪

948
00:43:35,720 --> 00:43:38,480
♪How many times must this repeat♪

949
00:43:38,480 --> 00:43:42,000
♪Sighs pull my gaze to retreat♪

950
00:43:42,000 --> 00:43:45,840
♪Sleepless nights, risks untold♪

951
00:43:45,840 --> 00:43:50,640
♪None of it for my own soul♪

952
00:43:50,640 --> 00:43:52,080
♪Winds blew, rains poured♪

953
00:43:52,080 --> 00:43:53,960
♪Umbrellas broke, we soared♪

954
00:43:53,960 --> 00:43:56,040
♪Sky fell, ground shook♪

955
00:43:56,040 --> 00:43:57,560
♪Through dusk till dawn I stood♪

956
00:43:57,560 --> 00:43:59,520
♪Cars passed, dreams drowned♪

957
00:43:59,520 --> 00:44:04,920
♪Every stop's chain unbound♪

958
00:44:04,920 --> 00:44:06,960
♪Moon watched, stars blazed♪

959
00:44:06,960 --> 00:44:08,840
♪Lamps died, connections phased♪

960
00:44:08,840 --> 00:44:10,960
♪Held hands, laughed then cried♪

961
00:44:10,960 --> 00:44:12,240
♪Hearts froze, parts died inside♪

962
00:44:12,240 --> 00:44:14,880
♪Tried hard, spoke true♪

963
00:44:14,880 --> 00:44:16,880
♪Now I'm someone I never knew♪

964
00:44:20,000 --> 00:44:21,880
♪Love came, hate stayed♪

965
00:44:21,880 --> 00:44:23,400
♪I arrived, you frayed♪

966
00:44:23,400 --> 00:44:24,760
♪Voice cracked, tears burned♪

967
00:44:24,760 --> 00:44:26,760
♪Life lost, lessons earned♪

968
00:44:27,120 --> 00:44:29,360
♪Grew up, let go♪

969
00:44:29,360 --> 00:44:31,360
♪Why cling to old sorrow♪

970
00:44:41,760 --> 00:44:44,720
♪How many loops replay♪

971
00:44:44,720 --> 00:44:48,400
♪Sighs steal my gaze away♪

972
00:44:48,400 --> 00:44:51,920
♪Lost nights, bold bets♪

973
00:44:51,920 --> 00:44:56,560
♪Nothing for my regrets♪

974
00:44:56,560 --> 00:45:00,960
♪Winds raged, storms crashed♪

975
00:45:00,960 --> 00:45:03,640
♪Dawns broke, I held fast♪

976
00:45:03,640 --> 00:45:05,760
♪Cars fled, dreams fled♪

977
00:45:05,760 --> 00:45:11,240
♪Every route left dead♪

978
00:45:11,240 --> 00:45:12,760
♪Love left, hate stayed♪

979
00:45:12,760 --> 00:45:14,640
♪Voice gone, tears paid♪

980
00:45:14,640 --> 00:45:18,280
♪Grew strong, moved on♪

981
00:45:18,280 --> 00:45:20,280
♪Why dwell when it's gone♪
